{"tid":2058292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國警察示威維持秩序期間同示威者battle","createTime":"2020-06-10T05:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T05:26:00.000Z","uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0a856e69d4cdb9bb1bb3ae483b8e457d04bb79be","tid":2058292,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:09:26.000Z","msg":"美國非裔男子佛洛伊德（George Floyd）之死引發全美示威抗爭。伊利諾伊州埃爾金市36歲員警古鐵雷茲（Hector Gutierrez）日前維持秩序時，看見民眾圍成一個圈圈，觀賞1名男子隨著音樂跳起街舞，一時技癢戴著口罩加入尬舞行列，嗨翻現場，歡呼、尖叫聲不斷。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，影片中可見，古鐵雷茲看著該名男子有點挑釁似地以右腳在同伴面前劃一條線，當場脫掉背心、皮套，上前使出一連串高難度地板動作，包括大迴旋、單手伏地挺身等，最後再以謝謝觀眾賞臉的手勢作結，精采絕倫博得滿堂彩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/belinda.vega.39/videos/3678345285513307/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fbelinda.vega.39%2Fvideos%2F3678345285513307%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=3f8e660c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/belinda.vega.39/videos/3678345285513307/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3193177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3193177&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=b24209c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3193177&h=34287c4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3193177</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dailyherald.com/storyimage/DA/20200606/NEWS/200609156/AR/0/AR-200609156.jpg&amp;updated=202006070814&amp;MaxW=900&amp;maxH=900&amp;noborder&amp;Q=80\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyherald.com%2Fstoryimage%2FDA%2F20200606%2FNEWS%2F200609156%2FAR%2F0%2FAR-200609156.jpg%26updated%3D202006070814%26MaxW%3D900%26maxH%3D900%26noborder%26Q%3D80&h=53de1a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都幾癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dfc2